Disc.Title: PowerClear by PowerStop 24in and 17in Wiper Blade Set
Disc.Description: PowerStop™ is on a mission to deliver an easy and affordable way for any driver to upgrade their vehicle – no matter what and how they drive. PowerClear™ Windshield Wipers are designed to provide you maximum visibility for safe driving in all weather conditions. The wiper blades feature our quiet, streak-free RealView Advanced Rubber Technology for premium, long-lasting performance. PowerClear’s™ aerodynamic spoiler ensures even, consistent arm pressure at any driving speed. The beam blade design reduces ice and snow build up vs conventional blade design. The wear indicator shows when it’s time to inspect your blades for safe driving in rain, sleet, and snow conditions. Everything you need for a complete wiper blade upgrade is included with a windshield cleaning wipe and both driver/passenger wiper blades. For quick and easy installation, PowerClear™ Windshield Wipers have a vehicle-specific connection with no adaptors necessary.

Wash.Title: Meguiar's Gold Class Car Wash Shampoo and Conditioner Liquid 64oz
Wash.Description: Meguiar s® Gold Class™ car wash shampoo & conditioner is a rich and luxurious product designed to both wash and condition paint in one easy step. The premium formula gently foams away tough dirt, road grime and contaminants without compromising wax protection. Ultra rich paint conditioners clear away debris to reveal color and clarity, leaving paint looking radiant.

Wash.Title: Meguiar's Quick Wax Spray 24oz
Wash.Description: Meguiar's® Quik Wax® shine-as-you-dry formula provides dark reflections with increased gloss and shine that won't whiten on trim. Just mist on and wipe off to wax your entire car in less time than you thought possible. Use either when the paint is dry, or after washing/rinsing before drying. Now you can wax your car in just minutes, even in full sun!

Wash.Title: Turtle Wax and Dry Spray Wax 26oz
Wash.Description: Turtle wax® Quick & Easy™ Wax & Dry™ spray wax is the #1 selling spray wax and the easiest way to give your freshly-washed vehicle a deep, wet-looking shine while you dry it and leaves a highly reflective, streak-free shine with a silky-smooth finish

Wash.Title: Meguiar's Ultimate Quick Wax 24oz
Wash.Description: Now better than ever! Experience a glossier finish, increased protection, and more water beading action! No shade? No problem! Meguiar's Ultimate Quik wax can be used anywhere, even in full sun. In just minutes, get results you'd expect from liquid or paste waxes – spectacular shine, lasting protection, and relentless water beading – all in a fast & easy to use spray! With its non-whitening formula, Ultimate Quik Wax is clear coat safe and can be used on all paint types! And with Meguiar's Hydrophobic Polymer Technology, you'll get relentless water beading protection that lasts for weeks!

Wash.Title: Invisible Glass Cleaner Spray 22oz
Wash.Description: Cleans glass so well you'll think it's invisible! Contains no streaky soaps or dyes. Invisible Glass was developed with 2 simple objectives: superior cleaning power and invisible clarity. Invisible Glass is safe for tinted windows.

With an exclusive formulation using denatured alcohol and no ammonia, this product cleans thoroughly, dries quickly, requires no rinsing and leaves a pleasant, fresh aroma.
